            Part 1 Possible starting XI Lopez Carvajal Varane/Pepe Ramos Marcelo/Coentrao Modric/Illara Alonso DiMaria/Isco Bale/Jese Benzema Ronaldo Pepe had a stomach bug but he trained normally in the last training session. Arbeloa is out injured with a problem in the knee cap. Khedira is still out. Alot will depend on which players have recovered after the international break. Bale is expected to start ahead of Jese, Modric ahead of Illara, Varane ahead of Pepe and last but not least Isco might start instead of Di Maria due to the fact that Di Maria played the full 90 minutes midweek and might start from the bench. Levante is a strong team, well experienced with many of their players over 30. They are solid at the back and it is to be seen how the absences of their two main midfielders will affect them. They will sit back and just "park the bus" as many call the tactic of giving the ball to the opponent and defending with all men behind the ball and in their own 1/3 of the pitch.
